Subject: Re: [VB] re:anybody have a good heater

The rear heater tube (at) least on a 66 runs solely on the passide heat
exchanger. The driver side runs the long tube. Might as well leave them
both on. Curtains and seals and solid floors, OH MY! Make sure you have
german heat exchangers! My dansk HD ones (blobby alumn coating instead
or wonderful fins) sucked!

Al 66 dlx with m666 (ventilated front floor pan)


